high_descs: Turn right and stop at the left of the counter
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and stop at the counter to the left of the fridge
Slice the tomato on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Grab a slice of the tomato
Turn right and go to the fridge
Cool the tomato in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold sliced tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right, go across the room and face the counter on the right with the two lettuce.
Cut the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the slice of tomato in the fridge and pick the slice of tomato back up.
Turn right and go to the microwave above the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in front of the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to head towards the nearest counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right to walk to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Slice the tomato on the countertop.
Set the knife down on the countertop.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right to walk to the fridge.
Chill the tomato slice in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around and make a left to walk to the microwave.
Set the tomato slice down in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of tomato in the fridge to put in the microwave.
